Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's Explicitly Expose the "Simoun"{\i0}\N{\i1}Cast's True Natures on This Program{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:10.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Guests for the Milestone{\i0}\N{\i1}First Episode are These Two{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Monthly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,ADR!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:19.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bulletin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:27.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. My name\Nis Michi Niino, and I play Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:31.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm Rieko Takahashi,\Nand I play Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:36.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, so anyway...\NThe ADR Bulletin has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do a laid-back show, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:47.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are going to be ourselves\Nduring this time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:51.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm your MC.{\i0}\N{\i1}Just call me Simoun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,No-Holds-Barred!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:02.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,No-Holds-Barred!?\NBrutal, Live Talk Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:04.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:08.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a live session.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:16.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to turn over\Nthese cards one by one, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:19.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something written on the back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:23.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,So whatever turns up,\Nlet's give a laid-back answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:26.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,So here's the first card...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,May I pick the first one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:31.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll start with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:32.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:40.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is what I picked. Were you\Nuncomfortable doing explicit scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:42.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Starting with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,You turned it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:46.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll start this, huh? Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, I didn't really\Nhave any explicit scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:55.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I did have some\Nkissing scenes... We all did...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,All the sibyllae kissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:02.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But in my case,\Nmy scenes were all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:05.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not that\Nmy private life is totally normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,They weren't especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aer, your face is red{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,So now it's my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you ever fallen\Nin love with a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:34.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I went to\Nan all-girls' school, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:42.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,And there was an older\Nstudent who was a little boyish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,There was a time when\Nmy heart fluttered over that older girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,This happened a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, shall we move on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Okay, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I felt I'd get this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you had to think of\Na name for your pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:06.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:12.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,We fly the same Simoun, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and if we were to name it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know the Ri M_a_jon\NNeviril did today to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Diamond Ri M_a_jon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something funny about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:39.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a diamond! That's\Nan outrageous name for a pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:45.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It makes you think, "What kind\Nof pattern are they going to draw?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:50.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, personally,\NI'd like to go with "diamond"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:56.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who cares if you're sure.{\i0}\N{\i1}Just hurry up and make a decision!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's move on to the next corner!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why Oh Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why Oh Why!?\NSimoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:13.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this a quiz?\NSince it's called "Why Oh Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll be asked some questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:19.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and they'll test how much\Nwe've done our homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:27.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does pair mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,T-Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,To ride together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,To... ride... together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Teammate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it. Team...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pa... Pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Correct... Try to get{\i0}\N{\i1}some laughs, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where'd that come from?\NYou just heard a voice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard the voice of God just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:10.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's your partner when you fly\Na Simoun... That's your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now why don't you{\i0}\N{\i1}talk about the CDs?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:21.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'd like to tell you about Simoun's\Nopening and ending themes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the opening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:27.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...sung by Chiaki Ishikawa,\N"Utsukushikereba soredeii."\N("All You Have to Be Is Beautiful")
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's said it was\Nwritten with Neviril in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a very beautiful song,\Nand it's selling to wide acclaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, and this is the ending theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:44.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...performed by Savage Genius.\NIt's called "Inori no uta."\N("The Song of Prayer")
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the kind of song\Nthat touches your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:51.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I hope you give it a listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:57.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just about time to say goodbye...{\i0}\N{\i1}Make sure you close out the show!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess we were\Nlaid-back to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for\Nus to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer-chan, what did\Nyou think of today's show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:21.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Things I'd never known till now...\NOr rather things I should've but didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:24.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It cleared up a lot of mysteries,\Nso it was a good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you think, Neviril-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:32.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I think I'll make\Nsure I study up from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope you continue to watch Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't miss the next show!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't miss the next show!!{\i0}\NFade out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't miss the next show!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:50.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way they're going,{\i0}\N{\i1}I wonder if there'll be another show...{\i0}
